<h1 id="installing-on-linux" sourcefile="en/installation-and-upgrading/installing-nopcommerce/installing-on-linux.md" sourcestartlinenumber="8">Installing on Linux</h1>

<p sourcefile="en/installation-and-upgrading/installing-nopcommerce/installing-on-linux.md" sourcestartlinenumber="10">This chapter describes how to install the nopCommerce software on Linux system on the example of <em sourcefile="en/installation-and-upgrading/installing-nopcommerce/installing-on-linux.md" sourcestartlinenumber="10">Xubuntu 20.04</em>:</p>
